{"tid":729995,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"其實係咪，痛苦不幸，先係自然。幸福安全健康快樂美好環境，先係對抗自然？","createTime":"2018-07-05T04:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T13:15:32.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e6aee81322869b6183964d458982c3272d2cce80","tid":729995,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:50:27.000Z","msg":"自然環境，本質就係對人類和生物unfriendly<br />\n<br />\n自然環境，本身係對人類和動物都係仆街。<br />\n<br />\n自然，根本就係最醜惡和最可怕。<br />\n<br />\n想想，在自然法則下：<br />\n動物要互相捕食，先可以生存下去，否則餓死。<br />\n一個小小意外殺死你，你死左冇得復活重刷。（靈魂輪迴，天堂地獄未有百分百證據）<br />\n細菌病毒要食你細胞先生存到，搞到你成日病。<br />\n宏觀的天災，如颱風水浸地震海嘯暴風雪，又係好易ko你。<br />\n有醫藥發明，唔好開心住。因為所有藥，無論中西藥，都有副作用。<br />\n<br />\n人類就係抵抗自然，建設更好社會。<br />\n<br />\n社會對抗自然能力越強，越先進。"},{"pid":"1dfa65f011082b4e747283c348e606a1d5e85bc9","tid":729995,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:52:00.000Z","msg":"諗下點搵錢仲好啦 廢up傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2947265018770d1c61416bb2390a68883acb60cf","tid":729995,"uid":124941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1338bf328b638f838c5e8423298aaef633d992","tid":729995,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e554f2f1a94930b22e05b3e47b835f1a1a4b5589","tid":729995,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2947265018770d1c61416bb2390a68883acb60cf","tid":729995,"uid":124941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"re